properties.name: SBL_EL
properties.comments:
Deployment created on 2017-11-09. Previous active deployment for this site was listed under wrong SG (4812BB000334). Conditions of site on last visit are as follows: 
Panel angle-iron (attached to bottom) rusted off on 55 W panel and still holding but very rusted on 80 W panel. 4" (width) u-bolts were originally used to bolt into upper plates attached to panel, but these were replaced with 3" u-bolts that were originally used to bolt angle iron into catwalk grating. These 3" bolts appear to be made of different materials since they showed no sign of corrosion; however, it is recommended that these be replaced with better-fitting 4" bolts on next visit.
